Text: what you mean by AP, AB or BC????

pir8s003

don't bother downloading this if you don't know what AP,AB, and BC refer to...better yet, I think there's some AC/DC in there too, you might like that!
AP = advanced placement. AP classes are usually taken in high school for college credit.  AB is equal to the 1st semester of college calculus and BC is equal to a full year of college calculus.
